Lois Collier https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lois_Collier 0 Lois Collier (21 March 1919 – 27 October 1999), born Madelyn Earle Jones, was an American film actress born in Salley, South Carolina. She was sometimes credited as Lois Collyer. Lois_Collier ( 21 March_1919 – 27_October_1999 ) , born Madelyn_Earle_Jones , was an_American_film_actress born in Salley , South_Carolina .
